file.name: swagger-mobile.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Autify for Mobile API
  version: v1
servers:
  - url: https://mobile-app.autify.com/api/v1
    description: Production server
paths:
  "/projects/{project_id}/builds":
    post:
      summary: Upload a build
      tags:
      - Builds
      description: Upload the build file.
      operationId: uploadBuild
      security:
        - bearerAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: project_id
          in: path
          required: true
          description: The ID of the project to upload the build file to.
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          multipart/form-data:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                file:
                  type: string
                  format: binary
                  description: Build file.
              required:
                - "file"
      responses:
        '201':
          description: build created
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: string
                    example: yLA6m0oM
        '400':
          description: bad request
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  errors:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        message:
                          type: string
                          example: Error message.
        '401':
          description: bad credentials
  "/test_plans/{test_plan_id}/test_plan_results":
    post:
      summary: Run a test plan
      security:
        - bearerAuth: []
      tags:
      - TestPlans
      description: Run a test plan
      operationId: RunTestPlan
      parameters:
        - name: test_plan_id
          in: path
          required: true
          description: The ID of the test plan to run.
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        description: The build_id to execute the test plan.
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/RunTestPlanRequest"
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Test plan result created
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  id:
                    type: string
                    example: yLA6m0oM
                  test_plan:
                    type: object
                    properties:
                      id:
                        type: string
                        example: yLA6m0oM
                      name:
                        type: string
                        example: Test Plan Name
                      created_at:
                        type: string
                        example: '2021-05-18T02:44:55.978Z'
                      updated_at:
                        type: string
                        example: '2021-05-18T02:44:55.978Z'
                      build:
                        type: object
                        properties:
                          id:
                            type: string
                            example: yLA6m0oM
                          name:
                            type: string
                            example: App Name
                          version:
                            type: string
                            example: 4.0.0 0000
                          created_at:
                            type: string
                            example: '2021-05-18T02:44:55.978Z'
                          updated_at:
                            type: string
                            example: '2021-05-18T02:44:55.978Z'
                      execute_environments:
                        type: array
                        items:
                          properties:
                            os:
                              type: string
                              example: iOS
                            os_version:
                              type: string
                              example: '14.4'
                            device:
                              type: string
                              example: iPhone 12 Pro
        '401':
          description: bad credentials
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: http
  schemas:
    RunTestPlanRequest:
      properties:
        build_id:
          type: string
          required:
            - build_id
